WekaClassifierPanel - Class in gui
Panel for supervised Learning Implements WEKA wrapper for SVM and cross validation allows for grid search parameter optimization SVM models are trained on the currently active train view and applied to all images which are referenced within the train view To apply the SVM model to different images, the SVM model has to be saved and applied within the data management panel
